nodes.text: Ta'Veel was a male Defel, who worked for Thaereian Intelligence.

During the time of the Clone Wars, he was present on the space station Burnout, and he observed via a security camera an attempt by the Intelligence agent Xirossk to enlist the assistance of the Heroes of Cularin in helping him to defect. Ta'Veel used his comlink to contact his superiors on the station, to inform them of what he had seen.
